'''Taɣdimest''' neɣ '''Tamaziɣt n Ɣdames''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵜⴰⵗⴷⵉⵎⵙⵜ''') d yiwet n tutlayt [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tamaziɣ]] [[Tutlayin timaziɣin ticerqiyin|tasemrant]] yeṭṭafaren afurk n [[tutlayin tiznasin]] [[tutlayin tiznasin tisemranin|tisemranin]]. Tutlayt-a ttmeslayen-tt yimezdaɣ n [[amda|yimedwen]] n [[Ɣdames]] deg utaram n [[Libya]], di tlisa-ines yakk [[Lezzayer]] d [[Tunes]]. 

== Imsawalen ==
S unect n tensa n Ethnologue, llan wazal n 10,000 alamma d 13,000 n yimdanen yettmeslayen s tutlayt taɣdimest deg useggas n 2006, akken i llan wazal n 2000 n yimdanen niḍen yettmeslayen yis deg beṛṛa n tama n Ɣdames. Dɣa tutlayt-a d tin yettwaggzen s umihi n wengar s tseddaṛt n 6b.

== Asesmel asnilsan ==
Taɣdimest d yiwet n tutlayt tamaziɣt iy ggẓen (iḥerzen) aṭas n tulmisin tisnilsanin tisufin, dɣa amawal n teɣdimest yettwaskelsen sɣur n Lanfry immal-d asemdu idrusen seg tutlayt [[Taɛrabt|taserɣint]] (Taɛrabt).

